Dialogue: 1,0:22:53.60,0:22:56.10,Ending,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)\be2}V očiach sa odrážajú
Dialogue: 1,0:22:56.39,0:22:59.15,Ending,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)\be2}tisícky hviezd
Dialogue: 1,0:22:59.90,0:23:02.52,Ending,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)\be2}uchytené
Dialogue: 1,0:23:03.23,0:23:05.90,Ending,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)\be2}v srdci.
Dialogue: 1,0:23:06.82,0:23:09.24,Ending,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)\be2}Už sa viac nemôžeme stretnúť,
Dialogue: 1,0:23:09.70,0:23:12.33,Ending,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)\be2}tak som vydýchla
Dialogue: 1,0:23:13.12,0:23:15.66,Ending,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)\be2}tvoje meno
Dialogue: 1,0:23:16.54,0:23:19.17,Ending,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)\be2}a zatvorila oči.
Dialogue: 1,0:23:19.92,0:23:22.71,Ending,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)\be2}Existujú sľuby,
Dialogue: 1,0:23:23.21,0:23:26.13,Ending,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)\be2}ktoré sa nedajú dodržať.
Dialogue: 1,0:23:26.59,0:23:33.68,Ending,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)\be2}Keby si toho dňa bol stále taký nevedomý,
Dialogue: 1,0:23:34.47,0:23:40.81,Ending,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)\be2}tak by tvoj osud nebol pekný.
Dialogue: 1,0:23:41.15,0:23:47.36,Ending,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)\be2}Prekročila by som čas a išla za tebou
Dialogue: 1,0:23:47.82,0:23:53.91,Ending,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)\be2}a zvuk tohto hlasu by sa ozýval až na druhú stranu.
Dialogue: 1,0:23:54.03,0:23:59.33,Ending,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)\be2}Takže si večne prajem,
Dialogue: 1,0:23:59.92,0:24:06.05,Ending,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)\be2}aby tieto fragmenty prachu
Dialogue: 1,0:24:06.59,0:24:14.72,Ending,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)\be2}dohnali tvoje srdce.